### 健康检查
GET http://127.0.0.1:8004/health

### 写入一次模拟前端事件
POST http://127.0.0.1:8004/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "click_save_button",
  "source": "vue-page",
  "payload": {
    "page": "/orders/new",
    "component": "OrderForm"
  }
}

### 查询已写入事件
GET http://127.0.0.1:8004/api/events
